输入电压。该电路在vP=vN时输出发生跳变。而vP的电压表达式为：vP=vI*[R2\/(R1+R2)]+ vO*[R1\/(R1+R2)]，输出翻转时刻(vP=vN=0)的输出，即门限值为：VT=vI=-(R1\/R2)*vO=-(5\/15)*(±9V)= ∓3V。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">方波<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">-<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">三角波产生电路如图示，但是该电路有错误，其错误是<\/span><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">        <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">。<\/span>","answer":"<spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">C<spanstyle=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;font-size:12px;\">1<\/span><\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">的两个输入端接反了<\/span>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  D、电路中C1应该构成迟滞比较器，但现在R2引入的反馈是负反馈，不能构成迟滞比较器。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">图示电路满足正弦波振荡的相位平衡条件。<\/span>","answer":"wrong","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>图示电路中，选频网络为RC串并联网络，在中心频率点上，选频网络的移相为零，因此基本放大电路必须是同相放大器，图中，采用瞬时极性法判断基本放大器的极性：输入信号从T1管的栅极输入为正时，从T1的漏极输出为负，送入BJT管T2的基极，再从发射极取出，依然为负，因此基本放大电路的移相为180度，是反相而不是同相，所以电路不满足相位平衡条件。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">单门限比较器只有<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">______<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">个门限值，而迟滞比较器则有<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">______<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">个门限电压值。<\/span>","answer":"<spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">1<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">，<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">2<\/span>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  D、单门限比较器只有一个唯一的门限值，而迟滞比较器有两个门限值。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">带通滤波器的<\/span><em><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">Q<\/span><\/em><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">值越大，它的通带宽度就越窄（设它的中心频率远大于带宽）。<\/span>","answer":"correct","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>带通滤波器的Q值和通频带成反比，Q值越大，选择性越好，但是通频带就越窄。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">在采用正反馈方框图的条件下，如果正弦波振荡电路反馈网络的相移为<\/span><em><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Symbol;\">j<\/span><\/em><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">f<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">，放大电路的相移为<\/span><em><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Symbol;\">j<\/span><\/em><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">a<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">，那么只有<img src=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/6E81779100F5536D95BFE23E03EDE0FD.jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=520x520&amp;quality=100\"\/>，才能满足相位平衡条件。<\/span>","answer":"wrong","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>在采用正反馈方框图的条件下，反馈信号回到放大电路输入端口时没有反相环节，所以只有φa +φf =2nπ，才能满足相位平衡条件。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">希望抑制<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">50Hz<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">的交流电源干扰，应选用<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">______<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">滤波器。<\/span>","answer":"<spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">带阻<\/span>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  D、希望抑制50Hz的交流电源干扰，希望抑制的是某一个固定的频率，应该采用带阻滤波器，将带阻滤波器的中心频率设置在50Hz上。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">信号频率覆盖<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">500Hz~50kHz<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">，应选用<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">______<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">滤波器。<\/span>","answer":"<spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">带通<\/span>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  A、信号频率覆盖500Hz~50kHz，希望通过的为某一频带的信号，因此可以采用带通滤波器，将带通滤波器的上限设置为50kHz，下限设置为500Hz。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">单门限比较器只有<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">______<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">个门限值，而迟滞比较器则有<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">______<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">个门限电压值。<\/span>","answer":"<spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">1<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">，<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">2<\/span>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  A、单门限比较器只有一个唯一的门限值，而迟滞比较器有两个门限值。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">电路如图示，为了使电路能够起振，<em><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">R<\/span><\/em><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">3<\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">至少应该<\/span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">             <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family:宋体;\">。电路的振荡频率约为<\/span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">             <\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">。<\/span>","answer":"<spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">大于<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">1.3k<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Symbol;\">W<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">，<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">1kHz<\/span>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  C、为了使电路能够起振，必须满足A大于3，而增益为1 + [(R3+R2)\/R1] >3,因此R3>1.3k。<br\/>电路的振荡频率为：f=1\/(2πRC)=1061Hz≈1kHz。"}]